debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: During the experiment I was asked to click certain keys regarding the information as quickly as possible. Also, I was given a chpice to choose an object which has a certain amount of points behind it, the point of the experiment was to reciev information and learn what shapes gave what amount of points.
